services.title: Auaunaga
services.description: Auaunaga fa'apolofesa ma meafaigaluega e fa'aleleia ai lou fa'ata'ita'iga fefa'ataua'iga, e aofia ai polokalame fa'atau, fa'apogai a'oa'oga, ma lagolago maualuga.

affiliate.title: Polokalame Fa'atau
affiliate.description: Fa'atupega le tele o au feso'ota'iga e ala i la matou polokalame fa'atau atoatoa ma totogi fa'atauva lelei, siaki i taimi moni, ma meafaigaluega fa'asalalauga.

support.title: Nofoaga Lagolago
support.description: Lagolago fa'atau fa'apolofesa ma puleaina o pepa, gafatia talanoa ola, ma puleaina fa'apitoa o tala mo tagata fa'aoga maualuga.

faq.title: Fa'amaumauga Malamalama
faq.description: Fa'amaumauga atoatoa, fa'amatalaga, ma fesili masani e fesoasoani ia te oe e fa'aogaina lelei gafatia o le fa'avae.

insights.title: Malamalama
insights.description: Su'esu'ega maketi fa'apolofesa, malamalama fefa'ataua'iga, ma tala fatu mai la matou 'au faufautua tupe ma tagata su'esu'e maketi.
